{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5rSB5Luq_MTg5MQ_0005","text":"越怕偏越愛 錯誤又來 越錯偏越愛 痛也懶擋開","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","痛苦","執著","宿命"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["怕","愛","錯誤","痛","擋開"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,3,2,4,4,2,2,0,2,4,3,2,4,4,5,5,9,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyut6","paa3","pin1","jyut6","oi3","co3","ng6","jau6","loi4","jyut6","co3","pin1","jyut6","oi3","tung3","jaa5","laan5","dong2","hoi1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"越怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"偏越","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"錯誤","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"來","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"越錯","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"偏越","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"痛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"PART"},{"text":"懶","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"擋開","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「越怕偏越愛」和「越錯偏越愛」形成強烈對比，表達明知是錯和痛苦，卻無法自拔地投入，語氣帶有宿命感。"},"source":{"title":"死性不改","artists":["陳潔儀"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1891","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5rSB5Luq_MTg5MQ_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5rSB5Luq_MTg5MQ_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
